          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1657640566119-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> basmati rice</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> ground cumin </strong>and<strong> ground turmeric </strong>to the pan with your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and 300ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> [600ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>spiced rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1657640573862-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1657640573862-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1657640573862-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-copy-1657640573862-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
