          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1657640584326-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baharat chicken & pepper skewers</strong> over the <strong>spiced rice</strong></p><p>Drizzle over your<strong> natural yoghurt</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
